I had up during the demo,

00:30:50.000 --> 00:30:52.000
run some of the code and see how it feels for you.

00:30:53.000 --> 00:30:55.000
And I'll show you some resources after this

00:30:56.000 --> 00:30:58.000
where you can learn more about how to use tidy models.

00:30:59.000 --> 00:31:02.000
After that, we went on to deploy the model

00:31:03.000 --> 00:31:05.000
to Posit Connect using Vetiver.

00:31:06.000 --> 00:31:08.000
And as you saw, that really only took a couple lines of code.

00:31:09.000 --> 00:31:11.000
So we very quickly went from a final trained model

00:31:11.000 --> 00:31:15.000
to a model that's in the hands of users at our organization.

